<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="ATA31">
<l>makiḻti maṭaneñcē māṉuṭari ṉīyun</l>
<l>tikaḻti peruñcēmañ cērntā -yikaḻātē</l>
<l>yāreṉpē yēṉu maṇintuḻalvārk kāṭpaṭṭa</l>
<l>pēraṉpē yiṉṉum perukku</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Rejoice, ignorant heart, shine you too among humans,</l>
<l>you who have joined the great refuge. Increase yet</l>
<l>the great love that fell servant to him who wanders</l>
<l>adorned with anybody’s bones, without despising [them].</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
